org.apache.ignite.ml.tree.randomforest.data.impurity

Class MSEHistogram

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.tree.randomforest.data.impurity.ImpurityHistogram
      • org.apache.ignite.ml.tree.randomforest.data.impurity.MSEHistogram
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Histogram<BootstrappedVector,MSEHistogram>, ImpurityComputer<BootstrappedVector,MSEHistogram>

    public class MSEHistogram
extends ImpurityHistogram
implements ImpurityComputer<BootstrappedVector,MSEHistogram>
    Class contains implementation of splitting point finding algorithm based on MSE metric (see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mean_squared_error) and represents a set of histograms in according to this metric.
